column5: Earliest freeze on record for great lakes.  https://ca.news.yahoo.com/earliest-ice-record-appears-great-170122146.html
Saw that.  There's hope then for a full year of ice fishing in 2015.  For the first times since about 10,000 - 12,000 years ago.  Hooray!!!
I know after my 10th trip out ice fishing I can't wait any longer until spring.  Driving in the winter for 3 or 4 hours each way can be draining.  Hopefully it doesn't last too long.
I seen the ice on Superior......I almost puked    TDunn
